summary: The video shows several quick clips of people studying or in educational settings. The first clip shows a person in a library surrounded by books. The next clip shows a close-up of a report card with high grades. Another clip shows a young woman drinking wine and looking at a laptop, with a bulletin board behind her filled with notes and pictures. There is also a clip of someone holding textbooks and a keychain in what appears to be an elevator. Another clip shows a laptop screen displaying text in a library setting. Finally, a clip shows someone asleep on a stack of textbooks next to a backpack.
